y-200\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-1\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/?type=buy\">Buy</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/?type=rent\">Rent</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/sell\">Sell</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\">Manage Rentals</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/list-property\">Advertise</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md transition-colors text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/help\">Get Help</a></nav><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><a class=\"text-xs text-white bg-[var(--color-primary)] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-light)] transition-colors\" href=\"/login\">Sign In</a></div></div><main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto pb-16 lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"bg-gray-50 py-16 px-4 border-b border-gray-200\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">News</span><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2 mb-3\">Latest Updates</h1><p class=\"text-gray-500 max-w-lg mx-auto\">News, guides, and market insights from the MBPP team.</p></div></section><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-10\"><button class=\"px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium rounded-full border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 hover:border-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">All</button><button class=\"px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium rounded-full border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 hover:border-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Market Report</button><button class=\"px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium rounded-full border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 hover:border-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Platform Update</button><button class=\"px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium rounded-full border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 hover:border-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Guide</button><button class=\"px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium rounded-full border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 hover:border-[var(--color-primary)] hover:text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors\">Community</button></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-5\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-40 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Market Report</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400\">28 May 2026</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 leading-snug\">Kano Property Market Sees 15% Growth in Q1 2026</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Residential property values across Kano Municipal, Fagge, and Tarauni have risen sharply driven by urban migration and new infrastructure projects.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-40 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Platform Update</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400\">20 May 2026</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 leading-snug\">MBPP Launches Digital Rent Agreements for Tenants</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">New e-signature feature allows tenants and landlords to complete legally binding tenancy agreements entirely online without physical paperwork.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-40 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560518883-ce09059eeffa?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Guide</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400\">12 May 2026</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 leading-snug\">Understanding Rent Tiers in Kano: A Complete Guide</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">From budget-friendly flats in Fagge to premium homes in Kano Municipal, here is what you can expect at every price point.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-40 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524178232363-1fb2b075b655?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Community</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400\">5 May 2026</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 leading-snug\">New Agent Training Program Launches in June</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">MBPP introduces a certified training programme for new agents covering property law, customer service, and platform tools.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-40 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582407947304-fd86f028f716?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Market Report</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400\">28 April 2026</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 leading-snug\">Tarauni District Development: What It Means for Renters</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">New road networks and commercial centres in Tarauni are making the district one of Kano&#x27;s most attractive rental markets.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-40 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1564013799919-ab600027ffc6?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Platform Update</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400\">15 April 2026</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 leading-snug\">How MBPP Verifies Every Property Listing</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Behind the scenes of our verification process — from ambassador site visits to photo authentication and document checks.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-40 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560520653-9e0e4c89eb11?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Guide</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400\">2 April 2026</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 leading-snug\">Renting vs Buying in Kano: Which Is Right for You?</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">An honest breakdown of the costs, benefits, and trade-offs of renting versus buying property in Kano State.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-40 overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504384308090-c894fdcc538d?w=600&amp;h=400&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium text-[var(--color-primary)] uppercase tracking-wider\">Community</span><span class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400\">20 March 2026</span></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 leading-snug\">MBPP Partners with Local Banks for Rent Financing</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">New partnership enables tenants to pay rent in monthl